              <tr><td colspan="3"><b>Description</b><br>
Halas is the city of snow and Halas Heaters!  Rogues, Warriors, Shamans are abound here.  This is a rather small city compared to Qeynos.  Tradeskills available are baking, pottery, alchemy, and blacksmithing.  Enjoy my land and my people.</td></tr>
